could try to look the part.

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:10.934 position:24% line:89% align:start
Look the part huh?

00:04:10.968 --> 00:04:13.100 position:16% line:83% align:start
Like, could that pipe be
any more fake-looking?

00:04:15.501 --> 00:04:16.901 position:21% line:89% align:start
You sure look happy.

00:04:16.934 --> 00:04:19.601 position:19% line:83% align:start
You wanted to wear one
of those that badly?

00:04:19.634 --> 00:04:21.067 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah, of course I did!

00:04:21.100 --> 00:04:24.133 position:16% line:83% align:start
I mean, wearing the same
thing as Noel wears...

00:04:24.167 --> 00:04:27.467 position:13% line:83% align:start
