holding me nice and tight.

00:04:27.501 --> 00:04:29.901 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's the best ever!

00:04:29.934 --> 00:04:31.133 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Ninny] Gross.

00:04:32.968 --> 00:04:34.934 position:21% line:83% align:start
Well? We're in the
west district now...

00:04:34.968 --> 00:04:36.000 position:19% line:89% align:start
Do you feel anything?

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.801 position:16% line:89% align:start
Like personal feelings?

00:04:38.834 --> 00:04:40.100 position:30% line:89% align:start
No you dummy!

00:04:40.133 --> 00:04:41.300 position:19% line:89% align:start
More like the presence

00:04:41.334 --> 00:04:43.133 position:19% line:83% align:start
