but that's impossible.

00:04:46.167 --> 00:04:47.801 position:27% line:83% align:start
I just naturally
attract dragons.

00:04:47.834 --> 00:04:48.801 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's pretty random.

00:04:48.834 --> 00:04:50.267 position:7% line:89% align:start
