00:04:50.300 --> 00:04:51.801 position:19% line:83% align:start
that lets me
communicate with them,

00:04:51.834 --> 00:04:52.968 position:7% line:89% align:start
if that's what you're asking.

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:54.634 position:24% line:83% align:start
Then why the hell
are you even here

00:04:54.667 --> 00:04:55.801 position:16% line:89% align:start
cramping our style, man?

00:04:55.834 --> 00:04:56.801 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're useless!

00:04:56.834 --> 00:04:59.300 position:33% line:89% align:start
(explosion)

00:04:59.334 --> 00:05:00.334 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:05:02.467 --> 00:05:03.467 position:30% line:89% align:start
An explosion!

00:05:03.501 --> 00:05:04.801 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's bad.

00:05:04.834 --> 00:05:06.567 position:33% line:89% align:start
(whistling)

00:05:06.601 --> 00:05:07.801 position:30% line:89% align:start
