00:05:07.834 --> 00:05:09.067 position:27% line:89% align:start
"Looks like it"?

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:11.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
Aren't you gonna go
down there and check?

00:05:11.300 --> 00:05:12.834 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's out of our jurisdiction.

00:05:12.868 --> 00:05:15.133 position:16% line:83% align:start
Dealing with terrorists
is the police's job.

00:05:16.334 --> 00:05:17.334 position:35% line:89% align:start
Let's go.

00:05:17.367 --> 00:05:19.434 position:21% line:83% align:start
There's a chance it
might be a dragon.

00:05:19.467 --> 00:05:20.334 position:27% line:89% align:start
Well said, Noel.

00:05:21.801 --> 00:05:23.467 position:24% line:83% align:start
