00:05:27.968 --> 00:05:29.634 position:5% line:89% align:start
I just have to go there, right?

00:05:29.667 --> 00:05:30.667 position:35% line:89% align:start
That's it?

00:05:37.834 --> 00:05:40.434 position:19% line:83% align:start
This is the Realist's
headquarters.

00:05:40.467 --> 00:05:42.901 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah you could see that
from where we were.

00:05:42.934 --> 00:05:45.434 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's why I didn't
wanna bother coming.

00:05:45.467 --> 00:05:46.234 position:33% line:89% align:start
The Realist?

00:05:46.267 --> 00:05:47.634 position:19% line:89% align:start
You mean the tabloid?

00:05:48.767 --> 00:05:49.801 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:05:49.834 --> 00:05:50.934 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Huh...
-Ninny, over here.

00:05:50.968 --> 00:05:53.133 position:24% line:83% align:start
The other day, they
did a piece on you.

00:05:53.167 --> 00:05:55.634 position:10% line:83% align:start
