were calling Macy annoying

00:06:03.200 --> 00:06:05.767 position:7% line:83% align:start
after she left the group,
like you hated her and stuff.

00:06:06.934 --> 00:06:08.100 position:33% line:89% align:start
Interesting.

00:06:08.133 --> 00:06:10.334 position:16% line:83% align:start
So that's how the media
ended up spinning it.

00:06:11.868 --> 00:06:14.234 position:21% line:83% align:start
