to be anyone inside.

00:06:14.267 --> 00:06:16.133 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, it is a Saturday.

00:06:16.167 --> 00:06:18.167 position:7% line:89% align:start
Not that our boss even cares.

00:06:19.434 --> 00:06:20.434 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:06:23.501 --> 00:06:24.501 position:35% line:89% align:start
Marshal!

00:06:29.334 --> 00:06:30.334 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ninny?

00:06:31.334 --> 00:06:32.634 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm going.

00:06:32.667 --> 00:06:34.133 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Balgo] I'll come too!

00:06:34.167 --> 00:06:36.467 position:10% line:83% align:start
This is dangerous, so please
keep your distance, Balgo.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.100 position:38% line:89% align:start
Aw man!

00:06:40.767 --> 00:06:42.467 position:27% line:89% align:start
(glass shatters)

00:06:42.501 --> 00:06:44.601 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:06:52.667 --> 00:06:55.601 position:7% line:89% align:start
So, it was you I saw up here.

00:06:57.100 --> 00:06:58.300 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Macy] What...

00:06:58.334 --> 00:07:00.534 position:7% line:89% align:start
