00:07:01.567 --> 00:07:02.734 position:24% line:89% align:start
But that's my line.

00:07:02.767 --> 00:07:03.968 position:13% line:89% align:start
So let's cut to the chase.

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:06.133 position:21% line:83% align:start
What are you doing
in Reverse London...

00:07:07.934 --> 00:07:10.300 position:41% line:89% align:start
Macy?

00:07:10.334 --> 00:07:13.901 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Macy] This company wrote a
really mean article about us.

00:07:13.934 --> 00:07:16.300 position:19% line:83% align:start
They even said that
you actually hate me.

00:07:17.133 --> 00:07:18.567 position:16% line:89% align:start
