00:07:18.601 --> 00:07:19.968 position:24% line:89% align:start
You realize this is

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:22.000 position:19% line:83% align:start
the Realist's Reverse
London headquarters.

00:07:22.033 --> 00:07:23.968 position:16% line:83% align:start
