branch of the Realists

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:24.968 position:16% line:89% align:start
who wrote that article.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.801 position:27% line:89% align:start
Ugh, seriously!

00:07:26.834 --> 00:07:28.968 position:13% line:89% align:start
