00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:30.467 position:24% line:83% align:start
which twist things
out of context

00:07:30.501 --> 00:07:32.601 position:27% line:83% align:start
and make you look
like a bad person.

00:07:33.868 --> 00:07:35.601 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's why I came
here to destroy them.

00:07:35.634 --> 00:07:37.067 position:24% line:89% align:start
Honestly it's fine.

00:07:37.100 --> 00:07:39.634 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm used to that
kind of crap, really.

00:07:39.667 --> 00:07:40.968 position:38% line:89% align:start
Wait...

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:43.234 position:19% line:89% align:start
