00:07:48.934 --> 00:07:51.100 position:16% line:89% align:start
I didn't do any of this.

00:07:51.133 --> 00:07:53.033 position:7% line:89% align:start
This little one did it for me.

00:07:54.367 --> 00:07:55.667 position:33% line:89% align:start
A dragon...

00:07:55.701 --> 00:07:57.467 position:5% line:89% align:start
And it's already grown that big?

00:07:59.367 --> 00:08:00.701 position:41% line:89% align:start
Macy.

00:08:00.734 --> 00:08:02.133 position:24% line:89% align:start
Just give it to me.

00:08:02.934 --> 00:08:04.934 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Macy] She's not an "it."

00:08:04.968 --> 00:08:06.167 position:24% line:89% align:start
Her name is Elly.

00:08:07.300 --> 00:08:08.934 position:7% line:89% align:start
There's no way you'd know this

00:08:08.968 --> 00:08:10.200 position:21% line:83% align:start
since you're not
from Reverse London,

00:08:10.234 --> 00:08:12.400 position:13% line:83% align:start
so I'm gonna bend the
rules for you just a bit.

00:08:12.434 --> 00:08:15.701 position:13% line:83% align:start
But here, physical contact
with a dragon is a felony.

00:08:15.734 --> 00:08:18.801 position:5% line:83% align:start
As long as I keep my mouth shut
about this, you'll be fine,

00:08:18.834 --> 00:08:21.234 position:13% line:89% align:start
So please let me take it.

00:08:21.267 --> 00:08:22.100 position:35% line:89% align:start
I won't.

00:08:22.133 --> 00:08:24.167 position:24% line:83% align:start
Listen up, this is
for your own good!

00:08:24.200 --> 00:08:26.601 position:10% line:83% align:start
If they find out about this,
they'll have you killed!

00:08:26.634 --> 00:08:27.968 position:16% line:89% align:start
Why would I believe you?

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:29.934 position:21% line:83% align:start
Who taught me never
to trust anyone

00:08:29.968 --> 00:08:32.467 position:16% line:83% align:start
who tries to say, "this
is for your own good?"

00:08:33.667 --> 00:08:35.100 position:24% line:89% align:start
It was you, Nina!

00:08:42.334 --> 00:08:43.133 position:41% line:89% align:start
Elly?

00:08:44.667 --> 00:08:46.133 position:13% line:89% align:start
You don't look very happy

00:08:46.167 --> 00:08:49.133 position:21% line:83% align:start
considering we just
found our dragon.

00:08:49.167 --> 00:08:51.801 position:10% line:83% align:start
If I was happy after finding
out someone I knew did it,

00:08:51.834 --> 00:08:52.801 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'd be a psycho.

00:08:52.834 --> 00:08:54.033 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:08:54.934 --> 00:08:57.467 position:5% line:89% align:start
I see, so are you Macy Baljure?

00:08:57.501 --> 00:08:58.667 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:08:58.701 --> 00:09:01.601 position:5% line:83% align:start
You don't look like how I'd
pictured you, so I wasn't sure.

00:09:04.667 --> 00:09:07.434 position:19% line:89% align:start
Who the hell are you?

00:09:07.467 --> 00:09:08.734 position:27% line:89% align:start
(startled gasps)

00:09:08.767 --> 00:09:11.767 position:10% line:83% align:start
And why are you talking like
you're Nina's best friend?

00:09:11.801 --> 00:09:13.667 position:16% line:89% align:start
You have a lot of nerve!

00:09:13.701 --> 00:09:15.434 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm gonna murder you!

00:09:15.467 --> 00:09:17.234 position:24% line:89% align:start
(heavy breathing)

00:09:17.267 --> 00:09:20.000 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's awkward but she's
kind of in love with me.

00:09:20.033 --> 00:09:22.067 position:16% line:83% align:start
She does this when girls
are friendly with me.

00:09:22.100 --> 00:09:23.767 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's not personal.

00:09:23.801 --> 00:09:27.501 position:7% line:83% align:start
She thinks I was being
friendly with you back there?

00:09:27.534 --> 00:09:29.300 position:24% line:89% align:start
(heavy breathing)

00:09:29.334 --> 00:09:30.734 position:10% line:83% align:start
-Where the hell did you go?
-Anyway,

00:09:30.767 --> 00:09:31.968 position:7% line:89% align:start
the direct approach won't work

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
when she's already
riled up like this.

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.834 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna try to go
in from the roof.

00:09:35.868 --> 00:09:38.467 position:16% line:83% align:start
You keep her distracted
from there, okay?

00:09:38.501 --> 00:09:39.467 position:33% line:89% align:start
Ninny, wait!

00:09:40.467 --> 00:09:43.000 position:33% line:89% align:start
(explosion)

00:09:43.767 --> 00:09:44.767 position:41% line:89% align:start
Ninny!

00:09:49.467 --> 00:09:50.934 position:38% line:89% align:start
Whoops.

00:09:50.968 --> 00:09:53.334 position:21% line:83% align:start
She flew way further
than I expected.

00:10:07.601 --> 00:10:10.334 position:16% line:83% align:start
What do you think
you're doing, Banx Jr.?

00:10:11.300 --> 00:10:13.434 position:16% line:83% align:start
And what brings you to
the Crown Council today?

00:10:13.467 --> 00:10:17.100 position:10% line:83% align:start
Oh, uh well, I was just
uh, taking a little stroll.

00:10:18.767 --> 00:10:20.567 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's pointless to lie to me.

00:10:20.601 --> 00:10:23.467 position:7% line:83% align:start
You probably realized your
subordinates were in trouble.

00:10:23.501 --> 00:10:24.467 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:24.501 --> 00:10:26.234 position:21% line:83% align:start
Did something happen
to em out there?

00:10:28.968 --> 00:10:30.467 position:24% line:89% align:start
On second thought.

00:10:30.501 --> 00:10:32.667 position:13% line:83% align:start
It would appear that I may
have overestimated you.

00:10:34.968 --> 00:10:37.067 position:16% line:83% align:start
Given that you are their
superior, after all.

00:10:37.100 --> 00:10:39.767 position:13% line:83% align:start
I think it would be wrong
if I didn't inform you.

00:10:40.968 --> 00:10:43.300 position:13% line:89% align:start
Last night at 22:00 hours,

00:10:43.334 --> 00:10:47.133 position:10% line:83% align:start
an order for the elimination
of Balgo Parks was issued.

00:10:47.167 --> 00:10:49.567 position:21% line:83% align:start
While it hasn't been
carried out yet,

00:10:49.601 --> 00:10:52.434 position:21% line:83% align:start
I hear Bangnyfe is
already on the move.

00:10:53.467 --> 00:10:55.601 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sure you're familiar
with the way he works.

00:10:55.634 --> 00:10:58.300 position:10% line:83% align:start
I would watch out for my
subordinates if I were you.

00:10:59.767 --> 00:11:00.767 position:24% line:89% align:start
Let's go, Arkvine.

00:11:01.834 --> 00:11:03.167 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Arkvine] Yes, ma'am.

00:11:07.167 --> 00:11:09.434 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, that ain't good.
I'll tell you that.

00:11:12.601 --> 00:11:14.067 position:16% line:89% align:start
She's not dead, is she?

00:11:14.100 --> 00:11:16.467 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'll have to write up
a report if she is,

00:11:16.501 --> 00:11:18.734 position:21% line:89% align:start
and paperwork sucks.

00:11:18.767 --> 00:11:20.467 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hold on, you are?

00:11:20.501 --> 00:11:22.634 position:21% line:83% align:start
Looks like you know
who I am already.

00:11:22.667 --> 00:11:25.033 position:13% line:89% align:start
Guess that's no surprise.

00:11:25.067 --> 00:11:27.267 position:24% line:83% align:start
But then I know who
you two are as well.

00:11:28.634 --> 00:11:29.734 position:24% line:89% align:start
Sorry, who are you?

00:11:29.767 --> 00:11:30.767 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:31.834 --> 00:11:34.100 position:10% line:89% align:start
His name is Bruno Bangnyfe.

00:11:36.868 --> 00:11:38.801 position:24% line:83% align:start
He's one of the
Top of the Horns.

00:11:38.834 --> 00:11:41.434 position:7% line:89% align:start
And the director of the Inks.

00:11:42.968 --> 00:11:45.801 position:24% line:83% align:start
But what the hell
is he doing here?

00:11:45.834 --> 00:11:46.801 position:35% line:89% align:start
Finally.

00:11:46.834 --> 00:11:49.100 position:5% line:89% align:start
At least someone knows who I am.

00:11:49.133 --> 00:11:50.801 position:21% line:83% align:start
You got some nerve,
pissing me off.

00:11:50.834 --> 00:11:52.033 position:30% line:89% align:start
But whatever.

00:11:53.834 --> 00:11:55.067 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's me.

00:11:55.100 --> 00:11:57.234 position:24% line:83% align:start
Dragon blockade at
Penfront Street.

00:11:57.267 --> 00:11:59.634 position:10% line:83% align:start
Get rid of all the
bystanders and clear em out

00:11:59.667 --> 00:12:01.934 position:21% line:83% align:start
with the exception of
the Wing Bind employee

00:12:01.968 --> 00:12:03.400 position:19% line:89% align:start
positioned down there.

00:12:03.434 --> 00:12:05.100 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't worry, you'll
be able to tell

00:12:05.133 --> 00:12:08.167 position:10% line:83% align:start
who the Wing Bind employee
is from his Piper's mantle.

00:12:09.801 --> 00:12:11.667 position:10% line:89% align:start
Take your hands off of him!

00:12:21.167 --> 00:12:24.167 position:7% line:83% align:start
And you detain that Wing Bind
employee when you find him.

00:12:25.601 --> 00:12:28.434 position:10% line:83% align:start
He's the mastermind behind
the dragon terrorist attack

00:12:28.467 --> 00:12:29.267 position:24% line:89% align:start
that just happened.

00:12:30.501 --> 00:12:31.467 position:35% line:89% align:start
I get it.

00:12:31.501 --> 00:12:32.767 position:27% line:89% align:start
So that means...

00:12:33.901 --> 00:12:35.567 position:24% line:83% align:start
You're the one who
ordered the chief

00:12:35.601 --> 00:12:37.133 position:16% line:89% align:start
to give him that mantle.

00:12:38.167 --> 00:12:40.400 position:16% line:89% align:start
Makes sense, doesn't it?

00:12:40.434 --> 00:12:43.701 position:7% line:83% align:start
A dragonclad with dragon
powers decides to get revenge.

00:12:43.734 --> 00:12:44.901 position:13% line:89% align:start
On the very tabloid office

00:12:44.934 --> 00:12:46.801 position:21% line:83% align:start
that turned him into
a laughing stock

00:12:46.834 --> 00:12:49.334 position:7% line:89% align:start
and made jokes at his expense.

00:12:49.367 --> 00:12:50.501 position:44% line:89% align:start
Eh?

00:12:50.534 --> 00:12:53.467 position:10% line:83% align:start
Not that I really care if it
makes sense to you or not.

00:12:53.501 --> 00:12:55.167 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're messed up.

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:57.100 position:13% line:83% align:start
I don't understand the
purpose of framing Balgo.

00:12:57.133 --> 00:12:59.434 position:16% line:83% align:start
What good could
possibly come from that?

00:12:59.467 --> 00:13:00.968 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, plenty of good!

00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:03.067 position:13% line:89% align:start
At 22:00 hours last night,

00:13:03.100 --> 00:13:06.067 position:7% line:83% align:start
a Punitive Dragon Designation
and Elimination Order

00:13:06.100 --> 00:13:08.067 position:10% line:89% align:start
was issued for Balgo Parks.

00:13:08.100 --> 00:13:11.734 position:10% line:83% align:start
In just a few hours there'll
be a bounty on his head.

00:13:11.767 --> 00:13:12.968 position:13% line:89% align:start
And whoever takes him out

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:15.801 position:19% line:83% align:start
will secure themselves
a guaranteed place

00:13:15.834 --> 00:13:18.267 position:13% line:89% align:start
in Reverse London history.

00:13:18.300 --> 00:13:19.467 position:38% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:13:19.501 --> 00:13:22.400 position:10% line:83% align:start
So for the time being, I'll
just be taking the guy in.

00:13:22.434 --> 00:13:24.567 position:16% line:83% align:start
But as soon as the
order goes into effect,

00:13:24.601 --> 00:13:26.067 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'll kill him on the spot.

00:13:27.501 --> 00:13:29.801 position:19% line:83% align:start
Don't even try crying
or negotiating.

00:13:29.834 --> 00:13:33.467 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm still working under the
Dragon Contact Prohibition Law.

00:13:33.501 --> 00:13:35.000 position:24% line:89% align:start
Like I said before,

00:13:35.033 --> 00:13:37.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't plan on taking
the two of you out,

00:13:38.133 --> 00:13:40.467 position:21% line:83% align:start
as long as you
stay out of my way.

00:13:40.501 --> 00:13:42.300 position:24% line:89% align:start
Excuse me, Bruno.

00:13:42.334 --> 00:13:43.133 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:44.234 --> 00:13:46.601 position:19% line:83% align:start
You have the worst dye
job I've ever seen.

00:13:46.634 --> 00:13:48.400 position:16% line:89% align:start
The hell'd you just say?

00:13:48.434 --> 00:13:49.601 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'll kill you!

00:13:51.300 --> 00:13:52.734 position:41% line:89% align:start
Niiha!

00:13:52.767 --> 00:13:53.968 position:24% line:89% align:start
What's the problem?

00:13:54.000 --> 00:13:56.334 position:24% line:83% align:start
I did nothing that
requires scolding.

00:13:56.367 --> 00:13:57.167 position:33% line:89% align:start
I know that!

00:13:58.501 --> 00:14:01.567 position:13% line:83% align:start
I was gonna compliment you
and say "nice burn" there.

00:14:01.601 --> 00:14:04.334 position:7% line:83% align:start
Well, it didn't exactly
warrant a compliment, either.

00:14:05.501 --> 00:14:07.167 position:30% line:89% align:start
You know what?

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:09.734 position:10% line:83% align:start
I was trying to be nice
'cause you're just lackeys,

00:14:09.767 --> 00:14:11.467 position:13% line:89% align:start
but you had to get cocky.

00:14:11.501 --> 00:14:14.934 position:5% line:83% align:start
This'll definitely be an
"accident on the job" situation.

00:14:14.968 --> 00:14:17.000 position:21% line:83% align:start
And it'll totally be
worth the paperwork!

00:14:18.501 --> 00:14:20.667 position:19% line:83% align:start
Wait, dammit, what the
hell are you doing?

00:14:20.701 --> 00:14:22.100 position:10% line:89% align:start
Why aren't you coming at me?

00:14:24.767 --> 00:14:25.934 position:38% line:89% align:start
Let go!

00:14:25.968 --> 00:14:26.934 position:33% line:89% align:start
You idiots!

00:14:26.968 --> 00:14:28.067 position:35% line:89% align:start
Look up!

00:14:28.100 --> 00:14:29.100 position:27% line:89% align:start
Put up a shield!

00:14:30.367 --> 00:14:32.601 position:33% line:89% align:start
(screaming)

00:14:34.501 --> 00:14:35.501 position:41% line:89% align:start
Magic?

00:14:39.634 --> 00:14:41.300 position:19% line:89% align:start
Get a picture, quick!

00:14:41.334 --> 00:14:42.734 position:41% line:89% align:start
Noel?

00:14:42.767 --> 00:14:44.868 position:7% line:89% align:start
You came to rescue lil ole me?

00:14:44.901 --> 00:14:46.801 position:5% line:89% align:start
Well if you look at it that way.

00:14:46.834 --> 00:14:49.567 position:13% line:83% align:start
Then yes, you were rescued
as a result of my actions.

00:14:49.601 --> 00:14:50.934 position:35% line:89% align:start
Awesome!

00:14:50.968 --> 00:14:52.100 position:16% line:89% align:start
Though, full disclosure,

00:14:52.133 --> 00:14:54.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
I have no idea what's
going on right now!

00:14:54.300 --> 00:14:55.300 position:41% line:89% align:start
Go me!

00:14:57.834 --> 00:14:59.033 position:35% line:89% align:start
Damn it!

00:15:02.634 --> 00:15:03.501 position:21% line:89% align:start
I have one question.

00:15:06.133 --> 00:15:08.300 position:5% line:89% align:start
This isn't how it usually works,

00:15:08.334 --> 00:15:11.100 position:19% line:83% align:start
but I guess that's how
you Pipers operate.

00:15:11.133 --> 00:15:12.767 position:7% line:89% align:start
So are you the one responsible

00:15:12.801 --> 00:15:14.734 position:27% line:83% align:start
for bringing Macy
to Reverse London?

00:15:14.767 --> 00:15:17.934 position:10% line:83% align:start
And why does she suddenly
have a dragon with her now?

00:15:17.968 --> 00:15:19.901 position:16% line:83% align:start
Why couldn't you just
keep it to one question,

00:15:19.934 --> 00:15:21.167 position:16% line:89% align:start
you greedy little brat?

00:15:23.601 --> 00:15:24.968 position:35% line:89% align:start
All right.

00:15:25.000 --> 00:15:26.767 position:19% line:83% align:start
I scouted her and
brought her over here.

00:15:27.834 --> 00:15:29.300 position:21% line:83% align:start
She'd somehow
managed to discover

00:15:29.334 --> 00:15:32.167 position:13% line:83% align:start
a baby dragon in Front
London and was raising it.

00:15:33.601 --> 00:15:36.434 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sure you want to pin
that dragon on me, too,

00:15:36.467 --> 00:15:38.100 position:24% line:89% align:start
but that wasn't me.

00:15:38.133 --> 00:15:39.467 position:16% line:89% align:start
Your little friend there

00:15:39.501 --> 00:15:42.100 position:10% line:83% align:start
is one of those rare
people born in Front London

00:15:42.133 --> 00:15:44.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
who happens to possess
a high amount of mana.

00:15:45.934 --> 00:15:47.167 position:27% line:89% align:start
She's a Watcher.

00:15:51.300 --> 00:15:54.133 position:7% line:89% align:start
Did you say Macy's a Watcher?

00:15:55.267 --> 00:15:58.467 position:5% line:83% align:start
She would've ended up in
Reverse London sooner or later.

00:15:58.501 --> 00:16:01.901 position:10% line:83% align:start
Just like you and your other
buddy Noel Niihashi did.

00:16:01.934 --> 00:16:03.133 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right?

00:16:05.133 --> 00:16:07.968 position:10% line:83% align:start
Pro tip: don't be so on
edge holding your Witch Kit.

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:09.767 position:19% line:83% align:start
What if it
accidentally goes off?

00:16:13.434 --> 00:16:14.667 position:30% line:89% align:start
What the hell?

00:16:20.434 --> 00:16:21.434 position:41% line:89% align:start
Nina!

00:16:22.501 --> 00:16:24.000 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Ninny] Marshal!

00:16:29.767 --> 00:16:30.767 position:35% line:89% align:start
No don't!

00:16:31.601 --> 00:16:33.100 position:10% line:89% align:start
No please, let me go, Nina!

00:16:34.000 --> 00:16:35.567 position:27% line:89% align:start
Just stay calm.

00:16:35.601 --> 00:16:36.767 position:35% line:89% align:start
I promise.

00:16:36.801 --> 00:16:38.334 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna take you
somewhere safe!

00:16:45.300 --> 00:16:46.300 position:41% line:89% align:start
Elly!

00:16:48.634 --> 00:16:51.267 position:30% line:89% align:start
(Elly shrieks)

00:16:52.434 --> 00:16:54.434 position:33% line:89% align:start
Balgo Parks.

00:16:54.467 --> 00:16:56.300 position:30% line:89% align:start
Macy Baljure.

00:16:56.334 --> 00:16:59.434 position:7% line:83% align:start
You're seriously taking those
two and tryna run from me?

00:17:00.834 --> 00:17:02.100 position:30% line:89% align:start
Rickenbacker!

00:17:13.100 --> 00:17:14.501 position:24% line:89% align:start
Talk about naive.

00:17:15.634 --> 00:17:18.267 position:30% line:89% align:start
(Macy sobbing)

00:17:23.434 --> 00:17:24.601 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, come on.

00:17:24.634 --> 00:17:26.767 position:21% line:89% align:start
Stop crying already!

00:17:26.801 --> 00:17:29.033 position:16% line:89% align:start
But I left Elly behind.

00:17:30.300 --> 00:17:33.133 position:13% line:83% align:start
I told you, we can't take
the damn dragon with us!

00:17:33.167 --> 00:17:35.167 position:24% line:83% align:start
They're dangerous
to normal people!

00:17:36.367 --> 00:17:37.601 position:41% line:89% align:start
But...

00:17:37.634 --> 00:17:39.167 position:10% line:89% align:start
Would you stop your whining?

00:17:39.200 --> 00:17:41.634 position:10% line:83% align:start
Y'know, this is exactly what
I can't stand about you.

00:17:41.667 --> 00:17:43.501 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh I knew it, Nina!

00:17:43.534 --> 00:17:44.634 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's my worst fear.

00:17:44.667 --> 00:17:46.801 position:5% line:89% align:start
You really do hate me after all!

00:17:46.834 --> 00:17:47.934 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:17:47.968 --> 00:17:49.801 position:21% line:89% align:start
For crying out loud!

00:17:49.834 --> 00:17:52.000 position:7% line:89% align:start
Why are you so damn annoying?

00:17:54.267 --> 00:17:55.801 position:16% line:89% align:start
We should be safe here,

00:17:55.834 --> 00:17:58.167 position:21% line:83% align:start
at least for the
time being, that is.

00:17:58.200 --> 00:18:01.133 position:7% line:83% align:start
I've set up a Cloth, so they
shouldn't be able to find us.

00:18:03.934 --> 00:18:05.434 position:33% line:89% align:start
I gotta ask.

00:18:05.467 --> 00:18:06.667 position:21% line:89% align:start
What happened, Macy?

00:18:09.434 --> 00:18:11.167 position:27% line:89% align:start
Nothing really.

00:18:11.200 --> 00:18:14.801 position:5% line:83% align:start
You knew I never really enjoyed
being a member of the group.

00:18:14.834 --> 00:18:17.100 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I knew.

00:18:17.133 --> 00:18:20.067 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm just tall, and they thought
I looked alright in makeup

00:18:20.100 --> 00:18:22.467 position:24% line:83% align:start
and happened to
be a good dancer.

00:18:22.501 --> 00:18:25.801 position:10% line:83% align:start
So they gave me cool
clothes and make up to wear,

00:18:25.834 --> 00:18:28.267 position:5% line:89% align:start
but I never actually felt cool.

00:18:28.300 --> 00:18:29.300 position:35% line:89% align:start
I get it.

00:18:29.334 --> 00:18:31.601 position:7% line:89% align:start
I figured that's why you quit.

00:18:31.634 --> 00:18:36.300 position:7% line:83% align:start
No, if that's all it was, I
would've quit a long time ago.

00:18:36.334 --> 00:18:39.934 position:16% line:83% align:start
But I couldn't quit
because you were there.

00:18:39.968 --> 00:18:43.133 position:13% line:83% align:start
And if I'd quit, I
would've become a nobody.

00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:45.000 position:41% line:89% align:start
But...

00:18:51.667 --> 00:18:55.000 position:19% line:83% align:start
Then two months ago I
found my little one.

00:18:55.801 --> 00:18:56.968 position:19% line:89% align:start
I don't mind the rain.

00:18:57.000 --> 00:18:58.000 position:35% line:89% align:start
Me either.

00:18:59.300 --> 00:19:01.133 position:5% line:89% align:start
She looked just like the dragons

00:19:01.167 --> 00:19:04.067 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'd seen in picture
books and cartoons.

00:19:04.100 --> 00:19:06.467 position:21% line:83% align:start
Apparently, no one
else could see her.

00:19:06.501 --> 00:19:09.667 position:10% line:83% align:start
So I thought I was imagining
things or losing my mind.

00:19:13.834 --> 00:19:16.300 position:19% line:83% align:start
But, then she started
drinking water,

00:19:16.334 --> 00:19:20.334 position:21% line:83% align:start
so I figured, yeah,
she must be real.

00:19:23.100 --> 00:19:26.300 position:21% line:83% align:start
I gave her some food,
and she ate that, too.

00:19:26.334 --> 00:19:28.100 position:13% line:89% align:start
I gave her lots of variety

00:19:28.133 --> 00:19:30.667 position:10% line:83% align:start
but she seemed to like
fruits and veggies the best.

00:19:31.801 --> 00:19:33.767 position:7% line:89% align:start
She didn't go to the bathroom,

00:19:33.801 --> 00:19:36.133 position:7% line:89% align:start
she just kept getting bigger.

00:19:36.167 --> 00:19:38.667 position:16% line:83% align:start
She started looking more
and more like a dragon.

00:19:42.601 --> 00:19:44.601 position:13% line:89% align:start
A dragon only I could see.

00:19:45.834 --> 00:19:48.100 position:21% line:83% align:start
I suddenly felt
like I was special.

00:19:50.167 --> 00:19:52.567 position:27% line:83% align:start
I know our songs
did really well.

00:19:52.601 --> 00:19:56.100 position:10% line:83% align:start
And you and the other girls
were amazing on stage.

00:19:56.133 --> 00:19:59.000 position:13% line:83% align:start
But I was the only one who
wasn't myself up there.

00:19:59.667 --> 00:20:02.000 position:24% line:89% align:start
(heavy breathing)

00:20:02.033 --> 00:20:05.033 position:16% line:83% align:start
I had fame, but outside
of that, I had nothing.

00:20:06.834 --> 00:20:10.634 position:7% line:83% align:start
Honestly, I'm not sure anyone
even noticed me up there.

00:20:14.334 --> 00:20:17.133 position:19% line:83% align:start
But, that all changed
when I found Elly.

00:20:18.701 --> 00:20:21.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
It felt like she gave
me some kind of power.

00:20:22.000 --> 00:20:24.234 position:7% line:89% align:start
I felt like for the first time

00:20:24.267 --> 00:20:27.267 position:19% line:83% align:start
I had the potential
to be someone special.

00:20:29.334 --> 00:20:33.100 position:10% line:83% align:start
Then he, Bruno, appeared at
my place late last night.

00:20:37.267 --> 00:20:40.767 position:13% line:83% align:start
He told me he desperately
needed me and my dragon.

00:20:40.801 --> 00:20:42.801 position:13% line:89% align:start
My time had finally come!

00:20:42.834 --> 00:20:46.000 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'd be taken somewhere special,
and be something special.

00:20:46.934 --> 00:20:48.734 position:19% line:89% align:start
Nina, I have to say...

00:20:48.767 --> 00:20:51.467 position:38% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:20:51.501 --> 00:20:53.634 position:35% line:89% align:start
(grunts)

00:20:55.434 --> 00:20:56.434 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yo.

00:20:57.267 --> 00:20:59.501 position:7% line:89% align:start
You guys need an extra minute?

00:20:59.534 --> 00:21:01.167 position:19% line:89% align:start
To say your goodbyes?

00:21:04.534 --> 00:21:09.334 position:19% line:89% align:start
(closing theme music)

